Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of analog-to-digital converters (ADC) with 1-bit amplitude resolution for energy-efficient signal processing systems. This topic falls under the field of information theory (cs.IT) and signal processing (cs.SP). The paper also discusses parameter estimation with state-space models, which falls under the field of control systems (cs.SY). Bayesian filtering and smoothing are also mentioned, which are topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and signal processing (cs.SP). Finally, the paper discusses the performance analysis of the system, which could fall under the field of multimedia (cs.MM) if the system is used for audio or image processing.
